    "Interestingly, utilizing online resources and open-sourced tools such as khan academy seems to be effective in enhancing adult learning.",
    "Overall, A-Learn based word clouds for different sentiments can shed light on teaching improvement, policy adjustment, etc., with special attention on adult learning rather than traditional learning.",
